  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/c2d09991d51da5d166e6cf2c2e9307c5.poster.avif?t=1668698476\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/c2d09991d51da5d166e6cf2c2e9307c5.webm?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/c2d09991d51da5d166e6cf2c2e9307c5.mp4?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colorful, unique drinks -- the more you progress, the more recipes you will learn.<br></li><li>After each round, spin for a random mod or event that will always keep the game unique and challenging.<br></li><li>Avoid permadeath! If you fail to pay your rent, you will lose the run and have to start over!<br></li><li>Save your progress and track your run history.<br></li><li>As you play through and earn more run victories, you will unlock new unique mods that will be added to your pool.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3dd94e8d00d583d3dbff84412140a117.poster.avif?t=1668698476\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3dd94e8d00d583d3dbff84412140a117.webm?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3dd94e8d00d583d3dbff84412140a117.mp4?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUMMARY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Work your way through rounds by serving customers to earn gold.<br></li><li>You must earn enough each round to pay your rent -- or else you're done for!<br></li><li>Save your extra gold to purchase new recipes and level up.<br></li><li>Reach the ultimate rank before you miss rent... or die :D<br></li><li>Every round will be affected by a random game mod. Tons of unique mods keep every round interesting! Some are good, some are bad, and some are just plain weird.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.poster.avif?t=1668698476\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.webm?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.mp4?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
