ent -- or else you're done for!<br></li><li>Save your extra gold to purchase new recipes and level up.<br></li><li>Reach the ultimate rank before you miss rent... or die :D<br></li><li>Every round will be affected by a random game mod. Tons of unique mods keep every round interesting! Some are good, some are bad, and some are just plain weird.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.poster.avif?t=1668698476\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.webm?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025000/extras/3fddc8e65cfe2214d8277e0746e3c73d.mp4?t=1668698476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
